title: Jenni 'JWoww' Farley, husband expecting baby No. 2
text:
Jenni 'JWoww' Farley, husband expecting baby No. 2 October 19, 2015 4:42 PM By FRANK LOVECE. Special to Newsday 
advertisement | advertise on newsday 
Former "Jersey Shore" star Jenni "JWoww" Farley is expecting her second child. 
Us Weekly said Monday that Farley, 29, and Roger Mathews, 37, announced the news at their wedding reception Sunday in New Jersey. 
advertisement | advertise on newsday 
The couple subsequently told Us Weekly in a statement, "Baby No. 2 is official!! We are expecting and couldn't be more excited. A wedding that was beyond a dream come true and baby No. 2 on the way, we couldn't ask for more. We are on cloud nine!" 
Farley, who also starred in the spinoff series "Snooki & JWoww," and Mathews had daughter Meilani Alexandra in July 2014.
